milestones.description: David Hemp has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Gibbons's 1
Chumney and Abdool Samad's 66-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 63 between Chumney and Geoff Barnett
Codrington and Umar Bhatti's 31-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Joe Harris and Abdool Samad
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (11) for BMUDA, going past Romaine
